NewsToStocks provides news sentiment analysis and stock correlation information
for EDUCATIONAL and RESEARCH PURPOSES ONLY. It is NOT financial advice, NOT
investment advice, and NOT a recommendation to buy or sell any security.

- THIS SOFTWARE DOES NOT CONSTITUTE FINANCIAL ADVICE. Nothing in this Software
  should be construed as a recommendation, solicitation, or offer to buy or sell
  any stocks, securities, derivatives, or other financial instruments.
- PAST CORRELATION IS NOT INDICATIVE OF FUTURE PERFORMANCE. News-to-stock
  correlations shown are historical patterns and do not predict future stock
  price movements.
- YOU MAY LOSE MONEY. Investing in stocks and securities carries significant
  financial risk, including the risk of total loss of capital.
- CONSULT A LICENSED PROFESSIONAL. Always consult a SEBI-registered investment
  advisor (India), SEC-registered advisor (USA), or equivalent licensed financial
  professional in your jurisdiction before making any investment decisions.
- The copyright holder, contributors, and affiliates bear NO responsibility or
  liability for any financial losses, missed gains, or investment decisions made
  based on information provided by this Software.
- This Software is not registered with SEBI, SEC, FCA, or any other financial
  regulatory authority and does not constitute a regulated financial service.

All stock tickers, company names, and exchange names are trademarks of their
respective owners. NewsToStocks is not affiliated with or endorsed by any
